'''Ifeɣmes''' (Asget: '''ifeɣmasen''') neɣ '''Tiggaz''' d talmest gar telmas n [[tuɣmest|tuɣmas]] i yellan deg [[aɣesmaṛ|uɣesmaṛ]] n [[Afgan|ifganen]] d [[timsuṭad|temsuṭaṭ]] s umata, yella ar zdat n uɣusmar Afellay d wadday

== Tawuri ==
Ɣer waṭas n [[timestuga|timestuga]] yakk d [[aramma|irammaten]] am ufgan ifeɣmasen gan d tuɣmas [[assezgi|yessezgan]] i wegzam n [[učči|wučči]], maca ɣer temcac d [[ugel|uglan]] iy gezzemen aksum d wučči acku ifeɣmasen-is meẓẓey-it

== Amdan ==
Amdan n ifeɣmasen d win yemgaraden  s unect (ɛla ḥsab) n telmest d twacult n uɣersiw, amdya ar ufgan (amdan) llan 8 n ifeɣmasen ma ɣer temsuṭaṭ iden am yimcac d [[ayis|iysan]] llan 12, ɣer [[timseɣẓaẓ|temseɣẓaẓ]] 4 . Ma ɣer [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] 9

